      • make

        public static Canvas make​(io.github.humbleui.types.Rect bounds,
                          WStream out)
        Returns a new canvas that will generate SVG commands from its draw calls, and send them to the provided stream. Ownership of the stream is not transfered, and it must remain valid for the lifetime of the returned canvas. The canvas may buffer some drawing calls, so the output is not guaranteed to be valid or complete until the canvas instance is deleted.
        Parameters:
        bounds - defines an initial SVG viewport (viewBox attribute on the root SVG element).
        out - stream SVG commands will be written to
        Returns:
        new Canvas

public static @NotNull Canvas make​(@NotNull
                                   @NotNull io.github.humbleui.types.Rect bounds,

                                   boolean convertTextToPaths,
                                   boolean prettyXML)
        Returns a new canvas that will generate SVG commands from its draw calls, and send them to the provided stream. Ownership of the stream is not transfered, and it must remain valid for the lifetime of the returned canvas. The canvas may buffer some drawing calls, so the output is not guaranteed to be valid or complete until the canvas instance is deleted.
        Parameters:
        bounds - defines an initial SVG viewport (viewBox attribute on the root SVG element).
        out - stream SVG commands will be written to
        convertTextToPaths - emit text as <path>s
        prettyXML - add newlines and tabs in output
        Returns:
        new Canvas
